# API Conventions

Route handlers in `src/app/api/` delegate to `src/lib/api/`.

```typescript
// ✅ Route: thin handler
export async function GET(req: NextRequest) {
  const result = await getPostsWithReactions({ page, limit });
  return NextResponse.json(result);
}

// ✅ Logic lives in lib/api
// src/lib/api/posts/queries.ts
```

- Document routes with JSDoc `@openapi` tags (summary, `@description`, `@tag`)
- Use `export const dynamic = "force-dynamic"` on API routes
- Validate with Zod schemas from `src/lib/db/schema/`
- Regenerate OpenAPI after changes: `bun run openapi:generate`
- Action-based POST bodies use `{ action: "view" | "reaction" | ... }` pattern
